posts.name: Gaspers Patio Bar and Grill
posts.note: Gaspers Patio Bar and Grill is a long-standing family-owned bar for pub grub, beer, and live music in a festive indoor/outdoor setting. You have to get the Cuban sandwich.

posts.name: Satchel's Pizza
posts.note: Satchel's Pizza is a quirky cash-only institution is featuring thin-crust pies, salads, and calzones, plus outdoor seating. You need to watch Less Films video series on Satchel's Pizza.
